high_descs: Turn right, go straight, turn right, go forward, then turn left to approach the window.
Pick up the watering can on the floor in front of the window, to the left of the plant.
Turn left, go forward, turn left, walk to the wall, then turn left to approach the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at a watering can in lamp light.

high_descs: Go right and the right again to face the plant on the floor.
Pick the pitcher up from the floor next to the plant.
Go left and then left again and face the small table in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Turn a lamp on with a pitcher in hand.

high_descs: Move to the plant under the window to the left of the plant
Pick up the water pot from the floor
Move to the end table on the opposite side of the room
anns.task_desc: Inspect a water pot with a lamp
